data.description: Modern 3-Bedroom Home with Pool, Solar, And RV Parking in the heart of Hesperia, California. Home spans across 2,051 square feet of living space on an sprawling .66-acre corner lot. Upon entering, you'll be welcomed by an open designed layout that effortlessly merges functionality with comfort. The living room complete with an inviting fireplace, creates a warm atmosphere perfect for relaxed gatherings. The home has a very spacious kitchen Complete with an island, sleek countertops, and ample storage. Also features a pool for a cool dip on warm days and a covered patio offering an ideal setting for year-round outdoor relaxation. This property comes with two garages, The two-car attached garage offers convenient access to the main house. While the two-car detached garage with Half bathroom presents a unique opportunity, With the potential to be converted into an Accessory Dwelling Unit (ADU) used as a workshop. Another defining feature of this residence is its paid for solar offering significant energy savings.
